🔥 Production Scenario
Problem

A critical bug is fixed in the hotfix branch, but the fix is also needed in the develop branch without merging all hotfix changes.

Solution

Find the commit:

git log --oneline

Copy only that commit:

git checkout develop
git cherry-pick <commit-hash>

Push:

git push origin develop

This allows you to transfer only the required fix.

